Package jminusminus

Interface JLhs

All Known Implementing Classes:
JArrayExpression, JFieldSelection, JVariable
interface JLhs
The type of any expression that can appear on the lhs of an assignment statement: JVariable, JFieldSelection, and JArrayExpression.
